age Preferences  What you need to do...    Apart from all the fun and activity, there are things to do sitting down too.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not colour in some of our stars athletes?\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The challenge is part of the Olympic Federation of Ireland's 'Dare to Believe' programme supported by PTSB.\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It aims to open up the world of Olympic sports to Irish school children as well as teaching them about Team Ireland at the Olympics and celebrating French culture.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.76975017874839e-17, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The challenge is modelled on previous Olympic Games challenges like \\\"Road to Tokyo\\\" which saw 55,000 school children get more active while also learning about the wider benefits of sport and the Japanese culture.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999996855422, \"rank\": 3.143870089503684e-10, \"text\": \"Japanese culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1855,